{"tid":1778090,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"啱先收到ielts course推銷電話……","createTime":"2019-12-10T16:21:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T09:30:41.000Z","uid":311002,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e92828f5ce8d5cac44c25614eb09da4e3acc94c1","tid":1778090,"uid":311002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:21:29.000Z","msg":"是咁的，啱啱有唔知乜鳩升學調查打比我<br />\n，一開始佢問我讀大專定大學，咩科，跟住我就大大聲答佢香港大學精算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n跟住佢話errr..咩蒸蒜?搞到我要大大聲咁講理學士括弧精算學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n跟住佢講咗聲哦之後終於入正題，<br />\n問我英文咩成績，我開始覺得唔對路，<br />\n不過照樣大大聲答:<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">LEVEL3</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,跟住佢就話:吓你咁都碌入到大學，哦，係因為有3322先碌到入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n我心諗屌你老母咩叫碌入去，我差0.5分就upper quartile 啦屌你老母。之後佢就問我有冇打算報聽過ielts ,呢個時我終於意識到佢哋係嗰啲sell人報英文班嘅垃圾。我就答佢有聽到但唔會報，佢就好驚訝咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n吓你大學exchange intern 好多都要ielts 㗎喎，起碼都要6.5分，不過我地都建議有翻7分。好明顯想人問佢點算，我就答佢我唔會報，有需要時先考慮。正當我想屌佢sell人參加英文班嗰陣佢就好快咁唔該曬拜拜收咗線，我真係好撚柒嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"></span>"},{"pid":"d2aa6c6b8c70dd5c096827292217817c32a9ca6f","tid":1778090,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:25:09.000Z","msg":"太低汁<br />\n重作<br />\n<br />\n樓豬現實係咪讀I大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f094de9e9a0b233da83d670f0344dcb0db897c2d","tid":1778090,"uid":235702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f050503f863772a629b6e81a0241dc50132a88","tid":1778090,"uid":127177,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:28:59.000Z","msg":"Sell你條友分分鐘中學畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed04d30c20570e0beb8c8c81d162aa61a9bf8979","tid":1778090,"uid":72173,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:37:53.000Z","msg":"打個電話搵食姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc744e3214006e708d0b24abbc9cbd92c8c5bd7","tid":1778090,"uid":331192,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:41:31.000Z","msg":"有次又係呢啲電話打黎 <br />\n佢問我咩U <br />\n我答佢Kong U 然後佢問我係咪喺紅磡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a509f1e60cdee81d0d457ba861026b9fdf1a71a","tid":1778090,"uid":167330,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"48f050503f863772a629b6e81a0241dc50132a88","tid":1778090,"uid":127177,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:28:59.000Z","msg":"Sell你條友分分鐘中學畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:56:31.000Z","msg":"係事實，好多中學生等放榜嗰陣會去兼職打電話，嗰陣有好多朋友做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ede8f854e77acde4f638aa9d13afdae0f983c5","tid":1778090,"uid":108199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T06:45:56.000Z","msg":"以前聽過sale現代ielts<br />\n原來以前現代已經咁折墮靠電話推銷跑數"},{"pid":"a6e1665bef169e236b438456d87f6a743e4c3fd6","tid":1778090,"uid":116910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T06:59:27.000Z","msg":"之前打黎係個囡囡..<br />\n咁啱個陣得閒<br />\n後尾我同佢傾左半個鐘傾到完全唔關ielts事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25bfb757ace0a8631bcf38225e12a9d1ab84e711","tid":1778090,"uid"